# isCongruence

- _isCongruence(b, c, m)_

Answer `true` if _bâ‰¡c(mod m)_, else `false`.

```
>>> (40 + 35).isCongruence(15, 60)
true

>>> (40 + 35) % 60 = 15
true

>>> (9 + 7).isCongruence(4, 12)
true

>>> (9 + 7) % 12 = 4
true
```

